 32 Training Program as a Postdoctoral Scholar Fellow. She earned her PhD i
 n Epidemiology from the University of Washington in 2024. Her recent resea
 rch interests include understanding initiation and retention in treatment 
 with medications for opioid use disorder and preventing HIV and other harm
 s related to substance use among people who use drugs.\n\n\n4:00pm - 5:00p
 m\nIN-PERSON\nKeynote Speaker: Czarina Behrends\, PhD\, MPH\nTalk title: F
 rom Harm Reduction to Public Policy: Why HIV Prevention for People who Use
  Drugs is Still Important\nCzarina Behrends\, PhD\, MPH\, is an Assistant 
