 She is a trained epidemiologist who conducts quantitative and qualitative 
 research focused on improving harm reduction and health services for peopl
 e who use drugs. Dr. Behrends’ current work focuses on evaluating the pu
 blic health impact of innovative harm reduction and health services delive
 ry models for people who use drugs as well as estimating the as\n\nEvent U
 RL: https://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/TQZkJAa1Q8iXXvxxhY1h0w\n\n
