 cVQ$ has stood up several resources to support researchers and as they nav
 igagte UW's new Diversity in Clinical Trials policy: \nhttps://www.washing
 ton.edu/research/hsd/guidance/dct/. Join Jason Malone from the Human Subje
 cts Division\, Juliana Garcia from UW's Office of Healthcare Equity and Ch
 arlie Gregor from the Institute of Translational Health Sciences as they d
 iscuss the new policy and supporting resources\, including the new Communi
 ty-Based Research Collaboratory.\nFacilitators:\nCharlie Gregor\, MPH: Cha
 rlie has been with the Institute of Translatio\n\nEvent URL: https://washi
 ngton.zoom.us/meeting/register/1gmaHlIpSM2LbQo4xCNlMw\n\nSource: uw_cfar
